{"tid":1415070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家出去個陣睇睇呀！","createTime":"2019-08-05T13:10:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T13:39:33.000Z","uid":228311,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e28c52e019cdde9e8648e02880923d4acd677b55","tid":1415070,"uid":228311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:10:03.000Z","msg":"利申翻: 發夢每次都上前，前線玩核彈都唔撚會割<br />\n<br />\n其實香港真係有好多人都撐我地，好多人都好討厭呢個政權。所以我地有幾點要注意唔好令呢班人唔支持我地<br />\n<br />\n1. <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">態度真係要好少少呀</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我上到前個陣其實手足圍內都有禮貌同氣氛好好，但係對街外人都要好少少呀。好多手足一見到有人影相就即刻屌曬老母咁樣，其實真係唔係咁好。因為有部分都係遊客，或者係支持我地嘅，只不過係八掛同好奇影。<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">叫人唔好影相個陣不況態度好少少，加翻句唔該曬</span></span>，屌老母就留翻俾班狗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撘地鐵轉場個陣都要注意</span></span><br />\n<br />\n有手足撘地鐵轉場個陣鐘意大嗌口號嘅，我覺得完全冇問題。但係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果有小朋友或者老人家就要注意下</span>，因為冇人希望自己父母同埋小朋友嚇襯。所以我建議<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">每站嗌一兩次，或者淨係上車先嗌。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對準政權</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我絕對支持前線撚狗同埋屌狗，不過記住我地嘅目標係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求，甚至更遠嘅目標！</span>所以千奇唔好為打狗而打狗，記住我地係為左爭取乜嘢，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好令自己變左我地最憎嘅人。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，今日所有玩雞蛋，玩磚，玩火嘅手足我都唔撚柒會割架啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"41c0d22304eb5e95fb0235a31dbcde5dee819f07","tid":1415070,"uid":228311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:11:38.000Z","msg":"自推十萬次，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"b78f73407bceda546428e86264d1b277e3c02bc2","tid":1415070,"uid":228311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:14:04.000Z","msg":"自推十萬次，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"0a34ee219d5cbea154a1eeaad1a19e4d7d7ea5bf","tid":1415070,"uid":228311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:14:16.000Z","msg":"自推十萬次，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"8b3e775dcad3f38b7f7d248a270b6672b7ee172f","tid":1415070,"uid":228311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:16:34.000Z","msg":"自推十萬次，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"a3c73ca41cf92ba597adde8b8877e49b12112476","tid":1415070,"uid":228311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:16:56.000Z","msg":"自推十萬次，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"3ec58c54a1ebf75d8bf71e361c52e4ce51453d8a","tid":1415070,"uid":228311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:17:46.000Z","msg":"自推十萬次，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"108b59b37c9f0f107a0eb1e736afad70e2d74e06","tid":1415070,"uid":228311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:17:58.000Z","msg":"自推十萬次，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"3e71c8b422cde337b6810e433cb91490897f473e","tid":1415070,"uid":228311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:18:12.000Z","msg":"自推十萬次，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"e363298635d75bd79a9ace354221f4abce280b1a","tid":1